targets.query:
from(bucket: "team_data")
  |> range(start: -1h)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["sensor"] == "temperature")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "value")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> last()

from(bucket: "team_data")
  |> range(start: -1h)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["sensor"] == "humidity")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "value")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> last()

from(bucket: "team_data")

  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "value")

from(bucket: "team_data")
